Maintainer: The package maintainer <jafernandez@ksu.edu>
Description: cndcR is an R package of the manuscript "Minimum dataset characteristics for the 
    determination of critical nitrogen dilution curves using field experiments" The package contains 
    the source data and R codes used for sensitivity analyses to fit critical N dilution curves with 
    the Bayesian method.
